verbose_text: The protein expression levels of total protein kinase B (Akt), phosphorylated (p)-Akt, total glycogen synthase kinase (GSK) 3beta, p-GSK3beta, B-cell lymphoma 2 (Bcl-2), Bcl-2-associated X protein (Bax), caspase-3 and cleaved caspase-3 were detected by western blot analysis.
